r%20personal%20tastes%20and%20budget.%20Each%20service%20has%20its%20own%20selection%20of%20exclusives%2C%20so%20certain%20programs%20may%20make%20one%20platform%20more%20worthwhile%20than%20another.%20For%20instance%2C%20if%20access%20to%20every%20episode%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Office%26quot%3B%20is%20important%20to%20you%2C%20then%20Peacock%20is%20a%20must-have%20service.%20Conversely%2C%20if%20you're%20a%20big%20Marvel%20fan%20who%20wants%20to%20stream%20new%20shows%20set%20in%20the%20MCU%2C%20then%20Disney%20Plus%20is%20essential.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20comparing%20catalogs%2C%20we%20try%20to%20consider%20the%20range%20of%20entertainment%20offered%20by%20each%20of%20the%20best%20streaming%20services%2C%20how%20much%20the%20platform%20has%20invested%20in%20exclusive%20programming%2C%20and%20how%20much%20the%20app%20has%20to%20offer%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20a%20back-catalog%20after%20you%20burn%20through%20the%20originals.%20We%20also%20keep%20in%20mind%20which%20age%20ranges%20are%20best%20suited%20to%20watch.%20While%20most%20services%20have%20a%20rotating%20list%20of%20movies%20(for%20example%2C%20most%20Universal%20films%20will%20eventually%20find%20their%20way%20onto%20another%20streamer%20after%20Peacock)%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20consider%20which%20series%20and%20franchises%20remain%20platform%20exclusive%2C%20like%20%26quot%3BStar%20Wars%26quot%3B%20on%20Disney%20Plus%20and%20%26quot%3BStranger%20Things%26quot%3B%20on%20Netflix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOutside%20of%20programming%2C%20we%20evaluate%20streaming%20services%20based%20on%20several%20common%20factors%2C%20such%20as%20video%20and%20audio%20quality%2C%20app%20functionality%2C%20and%20price.%20On%20the%20low%20end%2C%20popular%20streaming%20services%20start%20at%20%248%20a%20month%20for%20ad-supported%20plans%20and%20can%20cost%20as%20much%20as%20%2425%20a%20month%20for%20ad-free%20plans%20with%20the%20most%20features.%20However%2C%20several%20services%2C%20like%20Disney%20Plus%20and%20Hul