0the%20brain's%20ventricles%2C%20or%20fluid-filled%20chambers.%20The%20buildup%20creates%20pressure%20on%20brain%20tissue%2C%20leading%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthree-concussions-turning-point-for-brain-injury-study-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebrain%20damage%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20left%20untreated.%20NPH%20is%20more%20likely%20to%20occur%20in%20people%20over%2060.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20main%20types%20of%20NPH.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrimary%20NPH%20has%20no%20known%20causes%20and%20makes%20up%2050%25%20of%20cases.%20Secondary%20NPH%20is%20caused%20by%20other%20health%20issues%20like%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fconditions-symptoms%2Fwhat-is-a-stroke%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estroke%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fconditions-symptoms%2Fare-there-warning-signs-before-an-aneurysm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebrain%20aneurysm%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fintense-face-pain-was-brain-tumor-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebrain%20tumor%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Ftraumatic-brain-injury%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraumatic%20brain%20injury%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECommon%20symptoms%20of%20NPH%20include%20struggles%20with%20walking%2C%20balance%2C%20vision%2C%20memory%2C%20hearing%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-symptoms-you-are-struggling-with-emotional-dysregulation-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emood%20regulation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fconditions-symptoms%2Furinary-incontinence%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eurinary%20incontinence%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b15fd8a3-b224-4b9a-97a