nk%5C%22%3Edevastated%20in%202004%20by%20a%20tsunami%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20also%20the%20island%20where%20Bhaskar%20had%20previously%20initiated%20a%20monitoring%20programme%20for%20hawksbill%20turtles%20%E2%80%94%20the%20boat%20journey%20was%20proving%20too%20hazardous.%20It%20did%20not%20take%20more%20than%20an%20instant%20for%20Bhaskar%20to%20don%20his%20fins%20and%20enter%20the%20water.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhitaker%20is%20not%20surprised.%20He%20got%20a%20front%20row%20seat%20to%20Bhaskar%E2%80%99s%20love%20for%20adventure%20and%20going%20the%20extra%20mile%2C%20while%20the%20two%20often%20interacted%20during%20the%20development%20of%20the%20Madras%20Snake%20Park%2C%20quite%20near%20to%20IIT%20Madras%20where%20Bhaskar%20was%20studying.%20In%20fact%20Bhaskar%20is%20said%20to%20have%20spent%20more%20time%20swimming%20in%20the%20waters%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20than%20in%20the%20classroom.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC_xX0J9IwgA%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC_xX0J9IwgA%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC_xX0J9IwgA%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Emaho%20Films%20(%40emahofilms)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhitaker%20encouraged%20the%20students%20toward%20nocturnal%20beach%20walks%20to%20find%20olive%20ridley%20sea%20turtle%20nests%20and%20rebury%20these%20in%20a%20safe%20hatchery%20set%20up%20at%20the%20Cholamandal%20Artists%20Colony.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20rest%20of%20us%20at%20the%20Madras%20Snake%20Park%20were%20hung%20up%20on%20snakes%20and%20crocodiles%2C%20and%20it%20was%20Satish%E2%80%99s%20dedicated%20single-mindedness%20that%20made%20me%20suggest%20to%20him%20that%20India%20needs%20a%20Mr%20Sea%20Turtle%2C%20and%20he%20would%20be%20the%20ideal%20man%20for%20the%20job%2C%E2%80%9D%20Whitaker%20writes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhaskar%20seemed%20to%20take%20this%20advice%20to%20heart.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20his%20IIT%20degree%2C%20Bhaskar%20was%20hired%20as%20a%20field%20officer%2C%20in%20which%20capacity%20he%20worked%2C%20and%20impressed%20the%20WWF-India%2C%20which%20offered%20him%20his%20first%20grant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20on%2C%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F393290%2Fsave-wildlife-conservation-heroes-india-innovation-protection-success-stories%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etravels%20across%20India%20spawned%20a%20cycle%20of%20insights%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20the%20world%20of%20sea%20turtles%2C%20lessons%20which%20hold%20in%20good%20stead%20even%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20when%20turtle%20researcher%20and%20conservationist%20Ed%20Moll%20came%20to%20India%20to%20conduct%20a%20freshwater%20turtle%20study%2C%20Bhaskar%20stepped%20in%20to%20help%20survey%20the%20highly%20endangered%20Northern%20river%20terrapin%20(%3Cem%3EBatagur%20baska%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20which%20nests%20on%20coastal%20beaches%20