friendly.%20But%20there%E2%80%99s%20one%20major%20problem%3A%20no%20one%20wants%20to%20buy%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20recycled%20sand%20is%20a%20green%20alternative%2C%20most%20buyers%20still%20prefer%20virgin%20river%20sand%20%E2%80%94%20simply%20because%20it%E2%80%99s%20cheaper.%20While%20river%20sand%20sells%20for%20around%20%E2%82%B92%2C300%20per%20tonne%2C%20people%20are%20only%20willing%20to%20pay%20%E2%82%B9200%20for%20the%20recycled%20version.%20That%E2%80%99s%20a%20massive%20price%20gap%2C%20and%20it%20makes%20it%20tough%20for%20recycling%20businesses%20to%20survive%2C%20let%20alone%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20irony%20is%20clear%20%E2%80%94%20we%20know%20how%20to%20manage%20waste.%20We%20have%20the%20technology%2C%20the%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20even%20the%20intent.%20But%20unless%20the%20economics%20start%20making%20sense%2C%20many%20of%20these%20promising%20ventures%20will%20continue%20to%20struggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGovernment%20initiatives%3A%20A%20step%20in%20the%20right%20direction%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20recently%20taken%20some%20major%20steps%20to%20address%20the%20viability%20gap%20in%20waste%20management.%20The%20introduction%20of%20the%20Extended%20Producers%20Responsibility%20(EPR)%20rules%20in%202022%20mandates%20that%20producers%20are%20responsible%20for%20recycling%20a%20percentage%20of%20the%20waste%20they%20generate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20beverage%20companies%20must%20take%20responsibility%20for%20collecting%20and%20recycling%20the%20plastic%20bottles%20they%20use.%20If%20they%20fall%20short%2C%20they%20must%20purchase%20EPR%20certificates%20from%20recycling%20companies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3