lers%2C%20helping%20to%20bridge%20the%20financial%20gap%20and%20making%20their%20operations%20more%20sustainable.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20government%20has%20begun%20mandating%20targets%20for%20producers%20to%20use%20recycled%20materials%2C%20which%20will%20further%20stimulate%20demand%20for%20recycled%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELearning%20from%20Japan%E2%80%99s%20success%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20India%20looks%20to%20improve%20its%20waste%20management%2C%20many%20experts%20say%20Japan%20offers%20a%20great%20example.%20In%20Japan%2C%20it%20all%20starts%20with%20creating%20less%20waste%20and%20designing%20products%20that%20can%20be%20repaired%20and%20reused.%20Nearly%20all%20their%20waste%20is%20collected%20and%20processed%20efficiently%20%E2%80%94%20thanks%20to%20strong%20awareness%20and%20a%20deep-rooted%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F401397%2Fsneakers-kobsook-empowering-differently-abled-designers-aziz-kapapi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eculture%20of%20sustainability%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20India%2C%20the%20real%20challenge%20is%20building%20that%20same%20mindset%20and%20making%20eco-friendly%20habits%20a%20part%20of%20daily%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20prime%20example%20of%20this%20is%20the%20resistance%20in%20Kodungaiyur%2C%20North%20Chennai%2C%20where%20residents%20are%20protesting%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20waste-to-energy%20plant.%20They%20fear%20that%20such%20a%20project%20would%20make%20the%20area%20toxic%2C%20unaware%20that%20modern%20plants%20have%20negligible%20emissions%20compared%20to%20the%20harmful%20effects%20of%20open%20waste%20dumps.%20As%20Aditi%20Ramola%2C%20Technical%20Director%20at%20the%20International%20Solid%20Waste%20Association%20(ISWA)%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CLack%20of%20funds%20means%20waste%20takes%20the%20least-cost%20route%20to%20disposal%2C%20which%20is%20being%20dumped%20in%20